2007-09-18  Martin Lambers <marlam@marlam.de>

	* src/view_area.cpp: Do not fail on images where a channel contains 
	only a single value, and therefore min == max. Bug reported by Maik
	Keller <keller@fb12.uni-siegen.de>.
	* src/interpolation_selector.cpp: Disable interpolation by default,
	since this is a data viewer and not an image viewer. Bug reported by
	Maik Keller <keller@fb12.uni-siegen.de>.

